{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if anything, you wanted to get something, it was usually myself and my sister, because not everybody immediately knew that we were Jewish because we were young and blonde.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- And there were those rules and regulations that you can only-- cannot walk on the sidewalk where the Germans are walking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to walk in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were those horses, and there was-- you know, it was-- and it was something which was coming so unexpectedly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, here you are a person, for better or for worse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, they loved you or they didn't love you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Never thought of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, you didn't wake up every morning and think, I am a Jew and he's a Pole.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then suddenly-- you know, and I remember every single day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, of course, they took away all the Jewish businesses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father didn't have a big business, but he had this store, which was also taken over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- what-- what do you call it in English?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was actually, it was locked up so that there was-- my father had [INAUDIBLE] with a relative, one young employee.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember a few nights, maybe after midnight, my father and this young man, and I think my oldest brother-- there was a back-- back door, which I don't know whether there was also the seal or there wasn't a seal-- anyway, through this back door, they-- they stole and-- and stole-- literally stole out some-- I think I told you this, but all the materials.",
      "word_count": 67
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the cottons and-- and linens for sheets, for pillowcases, for beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because all those things you didn't buy ready made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was-- those [INAUDIBLE] that the peasants were wearing, what have you.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
